A **SIP (Systematic Investment Plan) calculator** estimates the future value of recurring monthly investments in mutual funds. Enter your monthly investment amount, expected annual return rate, and investment duration — the calculator shows your total invested amount, estimated returns, and final wealth value.

In India, SIP is the most popular method of investing in equity mutual funds. As of 2026, the average SIP return for large-cap funds over a 10-year period has been approximately 12–14% annually, though returns are not guaranteed and vary by fund and market conditions.
